---
title: American-Spiced Chicken & Roast Veggie Toss with BBQ Mayo
description: Get the bold flavours of American cuisine right in your kitchen! Just coat chicken breast with our All-American spice blend, roast a chunky veggie toss and drizzle a smokey BBQ mayo over the whole shebang.
